http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: Ohio's technology academic content standards serve as a basis for what all students should know and be able to do by the time they graduate from high school. These standards, benchmarks and grade-level indicators are intended to provide Ohio's educators with a set of common expectations upon which to base technology curricula.
